35:12.510 --> 35:14.307
COME ON.

35:14.410 --> 35:15.968
BE REAL WITH ME
ON THIS.

35:16.080 --> 35:17.809
I AM, I SWEAR.

35:17.910 --> 35:19.502
IF YOU LOST YOUR JOB
BECAUSE OF ME,

35:19.610 --> 35:21.441
IT WOULD MAKE ME
FEEL SO MUCH WORSE.

35:21.550 --> 35:24.189
IT REALLY WOULD.

35:42.700 --> 35:44.406
