35:53.150 --> 35:56.472
I JUST HAVE
TO BRUSH MY HAIR.

35:59.520 --> 36:02.785
NO.

36:16.370 --> 36:18.167
THAT'S REALLY
BEAUTIFUL.

36:18.270 --> 36:19.601
THAT'S PERFECT.

36:19.710 --> 36:22.770
JUST PUT YOUR FACE
IN THE LIGHT A LITTLE MORE.

36:25.780 --> 36:29.238
JUST A LITTLE BIT
MORE TO THE LEI-T NOW.

36:29.350 --> 36:32.319
OKAY, TRY NOT TO LOOK
SEXUALLY OBJECT IFIED.

36:33.220 --> 36:35.609
( hissing )

36:35.720 --> 36:36.914
YOU SICKO !

36:37.020 --> 36:40.729
COME HERE.

