WHEN YOU WERE A KID ?

37:27.040 --> 37:30.669
NO...

37:30.780 --> 37:33.101
HANG ON.

37:33.210 --> 37:36.941
( laughing )

37:45.760 --> 37:47.955
WOW, YOU CAN'T
EVEN SEE THE WOUND.

37:48.060 --> 37:49.322
WHERE WAS HE SHOT ?

37:49.430 --> 37:50.829
POINT BLANK
IN THE HEAD.

37:50.930 --> 37:52.192
OH MY GOD,
OH MY GOD.

37:52.300 --> 37:54.495
