SHOT HIM IN THE HEAD.

37:56.770 --> 37:57.862
OH MY GOD.

37:57.970 --> 38:02.373
COULD THEY TELL FROM
THE AUTOPSY IF HE SUFFERED ?

38:02.480 --> 38:05.347
I HAVEN'T SEEN
THE AUTOPSY.

38:05.450 --> 38:07.145
OH, I THOUGHT YOU
WERE IN ON ALL OF THAT.

38:07.250 --> 38:10.276
NO, WE'RE JUST...

38:10.380 --> 38:12.189
WE JUST TAKE CARE
OF THE FUNERAL.

38:12.290 --> 38:13.541
( gulping )

