NO.

40:15.240 --> 40:16.730
Are you clammy,
cold or sweaty ?

40:16.840 --> 40:18.944
YES !

40:19.050 --> 40:20.938
Do you have a history
of panic attacks ?

40:21.050 --> 40:22.312
NO... IS THAT ?

