probably send someone--

40:40.630 --> 40:42.734
NO, THANKS,
I THINK I'M OKAY.

40:52.910 --> 40:56.073
DAVID ?

40:56.180 --> 40:57.716
I'M HERE.

40:57.820 --> 40:59.981
YOU OKAY ?

41:00.090 --> 41:03.912
UH, YEAH,
I'M FINE.

41:09.560 --> 41:11.664
YOU DON'T
LOOK SO GREAT.

41:18.200 --> 41:20.236
I HAD A PANIC ATTACK.

41:24.950 --> 41:28.249
