I THOUGHT I WAS DYING.

41:28.350 --> 41:30.215
HOW HUMILIATING
IS THAT ?

41:33.290 --> 41:36.612
I THOUGHT I WAS DYING
WHEN I WOKE UP THIS MORNING.

41:39.660 --> 41:41.628
WHAT WERE YOU ON
LAST NIGHT ?

41:41.730 --> 41:45.791
I DON'T EVEN KNOW,
SOME "X"-LIKE THING.

41:45.900 --> 41:49.028
