REALLY STRONG.

41:49.140 --> 41:51.859
YEAH.

41:57.980 --> 42:00.801
IT'S FUCKED UP
TO GET CARJACKED.

42:04.650 --> 42:06.140
IT WAS MORE
THAN THAT.

42:06.250 --> 42:08.013
WELL, YEAH,
I CAN SEE THAT.

