THIS CUTE BOY IN DISTRESS.

42:40.190 --> 42:41.179
IT'S OKAY.

42:41.290 --> 42:43.884
I'VE FALLEN FOR LIKE
50 CUTE BOYS IN DISTRESS.

42:51.930 --> 42:54.296
BUT THEN
IT WAS LIKE...

42:58.000 --> 42:59.900
