TO REMEMBER SOMETHING

47:31.680 --> 47:32.942
THAT HAPPENED LESS
THAN A YEAR AGO.

47:33.050 --> 47:35.974
YOU FORGET THINGS THAT
HAPPENED YESTERDAY !

47:40.450 --> 47:41.610
LOOK, RUTH.

47:41.720 --> 47:44.883
