YOU KNOW, IT WAS JUST
BETWEEN ME AND THE FATHER.

49:06.070 --> 49:08.664
THIS OUTGOING
YOUNG MOTHER,

49:08.770 --> 49:11.568
WHAT KIND OF HELP
ARE YOU GIVING HER ?

49:11.680 --> 49:13.204
JUST LIKE,
CANS OF FOOD.

49:13.310 --> 49:15.870
OLD CLOTHES AND TOYS
AND STUFF...

49:15.980 --> 49:17.242
LIKE FROM
THE FISHERS.

