49:37.100 --> 49:38.032
OH, COME ON !

49:38.140 --> 49:39.539
YOU TELL YOUR WIFE.

49:39.640 --> 49:42.279
THE TRUTH IS,

49:42.380 --> 49:45.508
THIS IS SOMETHING I STARTED
DOING WHEN YOU WERE,

49:45.610 --> 49:50.445
YOU KNOW, NOT THAT
EASY TO TELL THINGS TO.

49:50.550 --> 49:54.987
WHEN YOUR OWN
FAMILY NEEDED YOU,

49:55.090 --> 49:56.751
YOU STARTED HELPING
SOMEONE ELSE ?

49:56.860 --> 50:00.421
SOMETIMES IT HELPS TO MAKE
YOUR OWN PROBLEMS SEEM LESS BAD,

50:00.530 --> 50:04.648
WHEN YOU HELP SOMEONE WHO'S
GOT IT EVEN WORSE THAN YOU.

