WHAT'S UP ?

50:52.850 --> 50:55.148
OH, I DON'T KNOW...

50:59.050 --> 51:01.086
ARE YOU OKAY ?

51:02.760 --> 51:04.716
I DON'T KNOW.

51:09.230 --> 51:11.698
MAYBE IT'S JUST
WHO I AM.

51:17.070 --> 51:19.265
DO YOU WANT
TO SIT DOWN ?

51:21.910 --> 51:25.175
